metadata.name: Express yourself as a Vulcano
metadata.description:
With this art, the artist says that a human must show his personality, not hide his emotions, and become the real hero of his life, who is not afraid to show himself in all his strength and power.

size^ 100*70. 
3D art mixed with fluid art and brush painted.
Acrylic, putty on canvas.

NFT + physical art is sent to the buyer!
